Description: Yona programming language compiler targeting LLVM
 Yona is a compiled functional programming language that targets LLVM.
 Features include algebraic data types, pattern matching, traits,
 persistent data structures (RBT sequences, HAMT dictionaries/sets),
 async I/O via io_uring, and a comprehensive standard library with
 27 modules and 290+ exported functions.
